"Emacs starts, Emacs sets it based on the system-wide default language, which "
"you can set in the @samp{Regional Settings} Control Panel on some versions "
"of MS-Windows."
msgstr ""
"MS-Windowsでは、Emacsを開始したとき環境で@env{LANG}がまだセットされていない場"
